About Us
About Us
Lakeview Golf Club is Palm Beach County’s premier executive golf course. It is a par 60 and spans 3,006 yards. This 1972 classic is in exceptional condition with phenomenal greens and is a favorite for beginners, senior golfers and juniors. The course allows walking 365-days per year and offers a snack bar to its customers. Lakeview is the home to many annual events, including the “Goblin” and “Jingle Bell Scramble” for juniors, the “11 at 5” and other charitable tournaments.
